<SYNC Start=2149347><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2149790><P Class=KRCC>
멤피스 벨은?
<SYNC Start=2150886><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2152326><P Class=KRCC>
